      • isAutoBlocking

        public boolean isAutoBlocking()
        Returns:
        the the auto block status of tank

        Tanks can be automatically blocked (to disable fuelling) based on the following conditions:

        • The Low Level Alarm is active.
        • There is a Tanker Delivery in progress - as reported by the Automatic Tank Gauge console (not supported by all ATG equipment).

      • isBlocked

      • removeEventListener

        public void removeEventListener(Tank.TankEventListener ev)
        Removes an event listener from the list of registered event listeners for the Tank class.

        Call this method whenever disposing object references in your application having links to this tank. It is highly recommended to call this method otherwise event listeners may still be registered, references maintained and will NOT be garbage collected.

        Parameters:
        ev - the Tank Event Listener to be removed
